</head>
<body>

<!-- ──────────── PHASE 1 — ACCROCHE ──────────── -->

<nav id="mainNav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
    <img src="img/extracted/inline-5f4e9e2f.png" alt="Rejoice" style="height:50px;width:auto;display:block">
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#principe">How it works</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sejours">Retreats</a></li>
    <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
    <li><a href="#qui-sommes-nous">About us</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.helloasso.com/associations/rejoice-63/accueil" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="nav-cta">Donate</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg-img" style="background-image:url('img/extracted/inline-c6c62fb9.jpg')"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">✦ French non-profit (loi 1901) — rejoice.ngo ✦</div>
    <img src="img/extracted/inline-f095e93d.png" alt="Rejoice" class="hero-logo">
    <h1 class="hero-h1">Take care of yourself,<br><span>take care of them.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Rejoice brings together two needs that seem worlds apart:<br><span class="hl">your need to restore yourself, and</span><br><span class="hl">that of underprivileged children on the other side of the world.</span><br>Here, the two nourish each other.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#sejours" class="btn btn-p">✦ See the retreats</a>
      <a href="#soutenir" class="btn btn-o" style="color:white;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)">Donate</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">↓</div>
</div>

<div class="impact-band">
  <div class="impact-band-inner">
    <div class="impact-stat"><div class="impact-num">200+</div><div class="impact-lbl">children supported</div></div>
    <div class="impact-stat"><div class="impact-num">2 years</div><div class="impact-lbl">of active engagement</div></div>
    <div class="impact-stat"><div class="impact-num">66%</div><div class="impact-lbl">tax deduction (FR taxpayers)</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ──────────── PHASE 2 — COMPRÉHENSION + CONFIANCE ──────────── -->

<div class="principe reveal" id="principe">
  <div class="principe-inner">
    <p class="s-label" style="margin-bottom:.5rem">The virtuous circle</p>
    <h2>The Rejoice principle</h2>
    <p class="principe-sub">A simple idea, a rare alchemy.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <h3>You travel</h3>
        <p>You join a small-group restorative retreat — La Poumerole (Auvergne), Nepal, Norway… A space to breathe, connect, come back to yourself.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <h3>You come back transformed</h3>
        <p>Authentic encounters, practical tools, surprises. You leave revitalized, with a new inner compass.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <h3>Children get supported</h3>
        <p>Part of your retreat directly funds our actions: schools, training centers, orphanages in India and Nepal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="principe-conclusion">
      <p>"By restoring yourself here, you help children there.<br><strong>Your well-being becomes their chance: that's the Rejoice principle!</strong><br>And that's why we don't look like any other charity!"</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="band reveal" style="background:var(--yellow)">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:none">
    <div style="position:absolute;width:400px;height:400px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--brown);opacity:.1;top:-150px;right:-100px"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;width:280px;height:280px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--brown);opacity:.1;bottom:-120px;left:-80px"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="band-in">
    <p class="s-label" style="color:var(--brown)">Choisissez votre façon</p>
    <h2 class="band-title" style="color:var(--text)">Two ways to join the adventure</h2>
    <p class="band-sub" style="color:var(--brown)">Whether you join a retreat or support from home, in both cases,<br>every euro goes directly to the field.</p>
    <div class="formula-grid">
      <div class="f-card std">
        <img src="img/extracted/inline-c6c62fb9.jpg" alt="Soutien financier" class="f-card-photo">
        <span class="f-badge std">Classic option</span>
        <h3>Support without traveling</h3>
        <p>You directly fund our field projects. Simple, transparent, 100% goes to the children we support.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>One-time or monthly donation</li>
          <li>66% tax deduction (FR taxpayers — see FAQ)</li>
          <li>Regular field reports</li>
          <li>Automatic tax receipt</li>
          <li>Secure payment via HelloAsso</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#soutenir" class="btn btn-o" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Donate</a>
      </div>
      <div class="f-card feat">
        <img src="img/extracted/panorama-8c969949.jpg" alt="View from La Poumerole" class="f-card-photo">
        <span class="f-badge feat">The Rejoice option</span>
        <h3>Travel &amp; help</h3>
        <p>You experience a transformative retreat in exceptional places. Your restoration directly funds children — both at the same time.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Small groups (~12 people)</li>
          <li>Authentic encounters &amp; surprises</li>
          <li>Practical tools to leave revitalized</li>
          <li>Coming back to yourself in exceptional places</li>
          <li>Your retreat funds our missions</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#sejours" class="btn btn-p" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">See upcoming retreats ✦</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="founder-short reveal">
  <div class="founder-short-inner">
    <div class="founder-short-portrait">
      <img src="img/extracted/inline-f5f6403e.jpg" alt="Laurent Perraud, président de Rejoice">
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="founder-short-label">Who runs Rejoice</span>
      <h3>Laurent Perraud</h3>
      <div class="founder-short-role">Founder &amp; president · former pro snowboarder, SME executive</div>
      <p class="founder-short-quote">"This is my commitment:<br>to be on the ground, the steward and guarantor<br>of the actions stemming from your generosity.<br>Every euro forwarded, every project followed through over time."</p>
      <a href="#qui-sommes-nous" class="founder-short-link">Discover the full story →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="founder-short-cloud" id="founderCloudMini">
      <div class="founder-short-cloud-svg">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 380 240" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
          <defs><clipPath id="cloudClipMini" clipPathUnits="objectBoundingBox"><path d="M0.158,0.833 Q0.026,0.833 0.026,0.646 Q0.026,0.521 0.092,0.479 Q0.079,0.417 0.079,0.354 Q0.079,0.208 0.171,0.167 Q0.184,0.063 0.276,0.063 Q0.329,0.021 0.395,0.042 Q0.434,0.008 0.487,0.021 Q0.566,0 0.632,0.063 Q0.697,0.042 0.75,0.125 Q0.842,0.104 0.895,0.229 Q0.987,0.25 0.987,0.396 Q1,0.458 0.961,0.542 Q0.987,0.583 0.987,0.667 Q0.987,0.813 0.895,0.833 Z"/></clipPath></defs>
          <path d="M60,200 Q10,200 10,155 Q10,125 35,115 Q30,100 30,85 Q30,50 65,40 Q70,15 105,15 Q125,5 150,10 Q165,2 185,5 Q215,0 240,15 Q265,10 285,30 Q320,25 340,55 Q370,60 370,95 Q375,110 365,130 Q375,140 375,160 Q375,195 340,200 Z" fill="rgba(245,200,66,0.12)" stroke="rgba(245,200,66,0.6)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="vidwrap">
          <video id="founderCloudVideo" src="REJOICE_ITW_FONDATEUR_FR.mp4" preload="none" playsinline></video>
          <div id="founderCloudFallback" class="vid-fallback">Vidéo<br>présentation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="founder-short-cloud-play" id="founderCloudPlay">
          <svg width="14" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 22" fill="none"><path d="M3 2L17 11L3 20V2Z" fill="#2C1810"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="founder-short-cloud-label">✦ Watch Laurent's video</div>
      <!-- la video EN 2026 est la : https://youtu.be/jghAEeAlSqE -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="testi-section reveal">
  <div class="testi-inner">
    <div class="testi-head">
      <p class="s-label">They lived it</p>
      <h2 class="s-title">Des aventures qui marquent</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-grid">
      <div class="testi-card">
        <p class="testi-text">"Je suis rentré de ce séjour avec quelque chose d'indéfinissable. Pas seulement ressourcé — transformé. Les rencontres, la simplicité, l'authenticité… je n'aurais pas vécu ça autrement."</p>
        <div class="testi-author">Matthieu R.</div><div class="testi-role">Séjour Auvergne, 2023</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card">
        <p class="testi-text">"I was exhausted, at the end of my rope. This retreat taught me to find myself again. No grand speeches — just real moments, simple tools, and a team that truly cares."</p>
        <div class="testi-author">Isabelle M.</div><div class="testi-role">Séjour Népal, 2024</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card">
        <p class="testi-text">"What struck me: you give and receive at the same time. Helping the children while rebuilding myself… that's a rare alchemy. I'd recommend it to anyone looking for meaning."</p>
        <div class="testi-author">Thomas V.</div><div class="testi-role">India retreat, 2023</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ──────────── PHASE 3 — SÉJOURS (parcours conversion 1) ──────────── -->

