      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="sejour-form-cta">✦ Send my request</button>
      <p class="sejour-form-note">Your message will open in your email client pre-filled — it will only be sent once you confirm.<br>Rejoice does not store any data through this form. <a href="privacy-policy.html" style="color:var(--terra);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(200,92,58,.3)">Privacy policy</a></p>
    </form>
  </div>
