        <div style="margin-top:1.8rem">
          <div class="cloud-wrap" id="cloudWrap">
            <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;pointer-events:none;z-index:2" viewBox="0 0 380 240">
              <defs><clipPath id="cloudClip"><path d="M60,200 Q10,200 10,155 Q10,125 35,115 Q30,100 30,85 Q30,50 65,40 Q70,15 105,15 Q125,5 150,10 Q165,2 185,5 Q215,0 240,15 Q265,10 285,30 Q320,25 340,55 Q370,60 370,95 Q375,110 365,130 Q375,140 375,160 Q375,195 340,200 Z"/></clipPath></defs>
              <path d="M60,200 Q10,200 10,155 Q10,125 35,115 Q30,100 30,85 Q30,50 65,40 Q70,15 105,15 Q125,5 150,10 Q165,2 185,5 Q215,0 240,15 Q265,10 285,30 Q320,25 340,55 Q370,60 370,95 Q375,110 365,130 Q375,140 375,160 Q375,195 340,200 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" stroke="rgba(245,200,66,0.6)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
            </svg>
            <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;clip-path:url(#cloudClip)">
              <video id="profileVideo" src="REJOICE_ITW_FONDATEUR_FR.mp4" preload="none" playsinline style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block"></video>
              <div id="videoFallback" style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C1810,#5C3D2E);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center">
                <span style="font-family:Caveat,cursive;color:#F5C842;font-size:.95rem;text-align:center;padding:1rem">Vidéo<br>bientôt<br>disponible</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="videoPlayBtn" class="cloud-play">
              <svg width="16" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 22" fill="none"><path d="M3 2L17 11L3 20V2Z" fill="#2C1810"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cloud-label">✦ Vidéo de présentation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="bio-para">Former pro freestyle snowboarder, then CEO of a 40-person family-owned SME — it was after years of searching for meaning in my various ventures that, in 2019, a rupture happened in my life. The time <em>"for others"</em> had come, and I refocused my new projects on discovery, hospitality, sharing, and humanitarian aid.</p>
        <p class="bio-para">I have travelled several times in recent years to demanding regions — India, Nepal, and others. I needed to be there in person, alongside the NGOs, to understand their needs and witness the remarkable work being done.</p>
        <p class="bio-para">That's why I decided to create <strong>REJOICE in 2024</strong>, to financially support NGOs abroad. What drove my choice was the <strong>extreme urgency</strong> some of these organizations face to fight a level of hardship that's hard to imagine.</p>
        <div class="cit-bio">
          <p>"This is my commitment: to be on the ground, the steward and guarantor of the actions stemming from your generosity."</p>
          <div class="cit-author">— Laurent Perraud, President of Rejoice</div>
        </div>
        <p class="bio-para"><strong>Help us</strong> by funding the non-profit one-time or regularly. I personally commit that every euro is forwarded and used to support all these beautiful human projects.</p>
        <div class="fiscal-box">
          <span style="font-size:1.8rem">💛</span>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:.2rem">Tax benefit (FR taxpayers)</div>
            <div style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted)"><strong>66%</strong> reduction (or <strong>75%</strong> under IFI). See FAQ.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.helloasso.com/associations/rejoice-63/accueil" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-p">💛 Donate via HelloAsso</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

